Source: pg-isok
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://codeberg.org/kop/pg_isok

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-isok
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-isok
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, postgresql-PGVERSION
Description: Query-based data integrity management and soft-alerting for PostgreSQL
 pg_isok stores SQL checks as data, executes them in batches, tracks changes in
 questionable rows over time, and lets operators defer or accept individual
 findings so later runs surface only newly interesting data quality issues.
